She’s an MCO fan and I was stoked that she wanted to hang with me and touch faces. She’s funny and kind and nice and pretty and also has the greatest and softest hair in the world. 

Link in bio to grab the products we used. We have restocked so you’re good to go. 

A yes I got so excited that I tapped the Xtendlash mascara on my boobs. 

Here’s a list of the products we used. 

1: Hydrating Facial Primer
2: Miracle Hydra Glow Oil-Free Foundation (Natural Tan)
3: Instant Camouflage & Contour Concealer (light)
4: Cheek & Lip Tint (Tango)
5: Highlight & Glow Stick (Champagne)
6: Waterproof Eye Define Crayon Eyeliner
7: Brow Fill & Set (Medium Dark)
8: Eyelash Curler, then XtendLash Mascara
9: Pout Gloss (Tickle)
